data: ADAPT: Select the Admin Role by clicking on the role block
Useful Commands: /gamemode 1- Sets creative mode for yourself
Tutorial: Start by right clicking the tutorial block
Missions: Use the nether stars to start/stop missions 1/2
/gamemode 2 This is the command participants play in.
If you need to get all participants in the correct gamemode, type:
/gamemode 2 @a (This will set your gamemode to adventure mode)
Do NOT move the positions of the nether stars in your inventory
